{
  "id": "63e64898349ba5001b23cdfa",
  "title": "合理論",
  "created": 1676036249,
  "updated": 1676036299,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63e64898349ba5001b23cdfa",
      "text": "合理論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036252
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b2",
      "text": "とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036254
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b5",
      "text": "[西田幾多郎]「[哲学概論]」から要約[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b7",
      "text": "のりしろ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b8",
      "text": "　[認識の起源は何か]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202b9",
      "text": "　　真理は経験によって知るのか、思惟によって知るのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202ba",
      "text": "　　これが「[認識の起源の問題]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202bb",
      "text": "　　歴史上「[真理とは何か]」よりも先に「認識の起源の問題」が起こった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202bc",
      "text": "　　 真理とは何かを論じる前に真理は経験によって知るのかどうかという議論が起きた？？[/villagepump/基素.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202bd",
      "text": "　　 そう[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202be",
      "text": "　　 \t真理とは何かの方がより根本的な問題なのに、[カント](1724-1804)の時代でもまだ「真理とは何か」に関して曖昧で、[ロック](1632-1704)による認識論の方が先であった、というのが西田幾多郎(1870-1945)の解説[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202bf",
      "text": "\t\t[ロック]が初めて[認識論]を組織的に論じた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c0",
      "text": "\t\tロックの問題は主に認識の起源の問題だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c1",
      "text": "\t\t認識の起源をどう考えるかによって3つの立場がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c2",
      "text": " \t\t[経験論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c3",
      "text": " \t\t[合理論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c4",
      "text": " \t\t[神秘主義]([直感主義])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c6",
      "text": "合理論とは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c7",
      "text": "　経験論とちょうど反対の立場",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c8",
      "text": "　[真の知識]は[理性]により中から与えられると考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202c9",
      "text": "　合理論の基礎を置いたのは[プラトン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202ca",
      "text": "　　[知識]を[知覚による知識]と[理性による知識]に分けた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202cb",
      "text": "　　[知覚による知識]は人や時によって異なる、だから[真理]ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202cc",
      "text": "　　真理は理性を通じて自分の中から見つけ出さねばならない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202cd",
      "text": "　　具体的にどうするのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202ce",
      "text": "　　　[イデアの想起]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202cf",
      "text": "　　今の言葉で言えば[同一性というイデア]は範疇([カテゴリー])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d0",
      "text": "　[デカルトの本具概念]もプラトンの[イデア]に類するもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d1",
      "text": "　[デカルト]から[スピノザ]や[ライプニッツ]が派生した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d2",
      "text": "　ライプニッツは[合理主義]を最も徹底した人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d3",
      "text": "　　[人間悟性新論]はロックの[人間悟性論]を合理主義の立場から批評したもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d5",
      "text": "[カント]「悟性と感性、両方必要。要はバランス」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036292
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d6",
      "text": "[西田 幾多郎]「悟性と感性がどう結びつくかが問題だろう」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036299
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036249
    },
    {
      "id": "63e64898aff09e0000f202d8",
      "text": "初出 [/villagepump/合理論]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036249,
      "updated": 1676036264
    },
    {
      "id": "63e648a1aff09e0000f202d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1676036258,
      "updated": 1676036258
    }
  ]
}